## Data setup

::: {.cell hash='evolmar-tidyverse_cache/revealjs/panel-chunk-dining_dbb28b34d53d1da3a2897dc7cae70e95'}

```{.r .cell-code}
dining <- 
tibble::tribble(
     ~area_type, ~district, ~coffee_shops, ~fast_food, ~fish_chips,
  "Residential",   "South",            2L,         3L,          1L,
   "Commercial",   "North",           12L,         6L,          4L,
     "Suburban",   "South",            2L,         4L,          3L,
        "Rural",    "East",            0L,         2L,          0L
  )
```
:::

:::




